Usage: specifyScanChainPartition [-help] -partition <partition_name> {-all  | {<chainName>}}

-help                           # Prints out the command usage
<chainName ...>                 # specify scan chains' name (string, required)
-all                            # specify all the scan chains (bool, required)
-partition <partition_name>     # name of scan partition to be specified
                                # (string, required)